comments: Lowry (MIA) pulls Bridges' (BKN) hand off of the ball, and the contact affects his SQBR on the perimeter.
Butler (MIA) legally contests Thomas' (BKN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Lowry (MIA) briefly grasps Simmons' (BKN) arm underneath the basket and immediately releases him as Simmons pursues the rebound.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his forearm towards Bridges' (BKN) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contests Bridges' (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Lowry (MIA) and Finney-Smith (BKN) come together underneath the basket and marginal contact occurs as Butler (MIA) simultaneously deflects the ball away from Finney-Smith.
Simmons (BKN) is moving alongside Herro's (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) deflects the ball away from Thomas (BKN), and any ensuing arm contact is incidental.
Herro (MIA) moves somewhat forward towards Thomas (BKN) and marginal contact occurs as Thomas spins away from the contact.
Lowry (MIA) brings his hand towards Finney-Smith's (BKN) arm, causing Finney-Smith to momentarily lose control of the ball before he quickly regains possession.
Richardson (MIA) jumps somewhat forward towards Finney-Smith (BKN) and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) is already in Thomas' (BKN) path and marginal lower body contact occurs as they separate.
Finney-Smith's (BKN) left arm makes contact with Adebayo's (MIA) arm as he is elevating for the shot attempt.
Bridges (BKN) never fully establishes the ball in the frontcourt, and he legally gathers the ball in the backcourt.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his hands towards Walker IV (BKN) and marginal contact occurs in the backcourt.
Richardson (MIA) momentarily applies his hand to Bridges' (BKN) side, and he removes his hand as Bridges moves to receive the pass.
Lowry (MIA) jumps along Bridges' (BKN) path and absorbs the marginal contact during his driving shot attempt.
Walker IV (BKN) fumbles the ball in the air and legally regains possession as he returns to the floor without resuming his dribble
Lowry (MIA) attempts to commit a take foul on Finney-Smith (BKN), and the contact is marginal.
Richardson (MIA) commits a take foul on Bridges (BKN).
O'Neale (BKN) and Herro (MIA) come together off ball and marginal contact occurs as they engage and disengage with one another.
Butler (MIA) places his hands against Finney-Smith's (BKN) chest and marginal contact occurs as Butler releases away.
Robinson (MIA) and Bridges (BKN) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs prior to Bridges' gathering the entry pass.
Robinson (MIA) commits a take foul on Bridges (BKN).
